{"type": "article", "id": 14330, "title": "捷克和波兰的边境上的这个小房子，是故意要倒下来的样子", "description": "像一顶戴歪了的帽子", "date": "2015-09-03T10:20:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15386, "name": "捷克"}, {"id": 15387, "name": "中欧"}, {"id": 15388, "name": "歪房子"}, {"id": 15389, "name": "林中小屋"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607123550Eba1XdK6RjDmHuIV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t最近，在捷克和波兰的边境上，<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/09/01/znameni-ctyr-completes-contemporary-chalet-krkonose-mountains-czech-republic/\" target=\"_blank\">出现了一个倾斜的小屋</a>，小屋像是快要摔倒了，又像是戴了一顶歪歪的尖帽子。<span>这小屋的名叫 </span>Chalet Saint Peter<span>，位于捷克 </span>Krkonoše <span>山的一个小坡上，原先的小屋又老又破，业主邀请布拉格建筑事务所 </span>Znameni Ctyr <span>原址打造了一个全新的小屋。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123545BjQpGFIrTZ7cLDY4.jpg\" title=\"倾斜的木屋\" alt=\"倾斜的木屋\" data-ratio=\"0.7921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>倾斜的木屋</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123546xq1B7cCAvfSVlD89.jpg\" title=\"另外一个角度\" alt=\"另外一个角度\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>另外一个角度</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123546STkYUzoPWKhq60iB.jpg\" title=\"像是要倒到山下去\" alt=\"像是要倒到山下去\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>像是要倒到山下去</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123547pBZzYTwKcH8ix3dP.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">外立面使用的是天然材料，时间久了会有铜绿，建筑师说这能让小屋掩藏在丛林里\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123548tHvFuWn0LQqJ7VU6.jpg\" title=\"橡木框架的窗户呈矩形\" alt=\"橡木框架的窗户呈矩形\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>橡木框架的窗户呈矩形</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123548xTKYH819LWrqsROp.jpg\" title=\"居住和用餐空间集中在一楼\" alt=\"居住和用餐空间集中在一楼\" data-ratio=\"1.478125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居室和用餐空间集中在一楼</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123549I91azqHdu7ZJbshk.jpg\" title=\"这里是用餐空间\" alt=\"这里是用餐空间\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这里是餐厅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123549lwM1xTDtjhgmvUAE.jpg\" title=\"室内的窗户\" alt=\"室内的窗户\" data-ratio=\"1.0859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室内的窗户</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123550DidAa5J01B94ogcP.jpg\" title=\"螺旋楼梯通往二楼\" alt=\"螺旋楼梯通往二楼\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>螺旋楼梯通往二楼，二楼是主卧和阅读室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t建筑事务所的 <span>Juraj Matula </span>说，“要充分考虑到功能性，也要让木屋和周围的环境相融合”，经过讨论和设计，小屋共有四层，两层在地下、两层在地上，花岗岩和云杉是基础建筑材料，外立面则主要使用了雪松木。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/09/01/znameni-ctyr-completes-contemporary-chalet-krkonose-mountains-czech-republic/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}